highlights.text: “Vidigal” by Lipe Gama is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Brazil at #18.
Sabrina Carpenter has the most spots on Viral Songs Brazil. “When Did You Get Hot?” is the highest at #24.
“P do Pecado - Ao Vivo” by Grupo Menos É Mais and Simone Mendes has been on Viral Songs Brazil the longest, at 126 days straight.
“BEBIDA DROGA E SEXO” by Mc Neguinho do Morro, MC Donzela, and DJ NDM is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Brazil, up 12 spots at #57.
